      "review_summary": "The PR adds OpenCode Go Zen balance-only fallback fetching/parsing/rendering, billing-server balance parsing, regression tests, a changelog entry, and a PR-specific CI artifact job for live retesting.\n\nReproducibility: yes. for the current review finding by source inspection: the optional-off fetch path can return a balance-only snapshot whose only value is providerCost, and the menu model hides .opencodego providerCost when optional extras are disabled. The original live Zen-only fix still lacks positive current-head proof.",
